00:41:27.557 --> 00:41:29.140
TOM STANDAGE: So the
retrieval of-- So

00:41:29.140 --> 00:41:31.010
that's involving
written documents.

00:41:31.010 --> 00:41:31.780
AUDIENCE: Written
documents, yes.

00:41:31.780 --> 00:41:31.890
TOM STANDAGE: Oh, brilliant.

00:41:31.890 --> 00:41:32.390
They-- yeah.

00:41:32.390 --> 00:41:36.350
So this is the kind of thing
that is being flushed out.

00:41:36.350 --> 00:41:37.980
That's what I want to find.

00:41:37.980 --> 00:41:38.585
Thank you.

