of the striking things

00:45:24.940 --> 00:45:28.014
about social networking
in the West as well today

00:45:28.014 --> 00:45:29.430
is that it's
extremely centralized

00:45:29.430 --> 00:45:31.050
and it's run by
private companies.

00:45:31.050 --> 00:45:33.760
So we treat it as though
it's a public sphere,

00:45:33.760 --> 00:45:34.620
but it's not really.

00:45:34.620 --> 00:45:37.606
