00:46:12.080 --> 00:46:12.860
how that changes.

00:46:12.860 --> 00:46:14.920
Because that may be
a historical anomaly.

00:46:14.920 --> 00:46:17.920
It's just that doing
timely, in order delivery

00:46:17.920 --> 00:46:21.820
