00:46:23.590 --> 00:46:25.180
And it didn't do
it terribly well.

00:46:25.180 --> 00:46:27.140
It was very slow.

00:46:27.140 --> 00:46:29.610
So there are advantages
to a centralized model,

00:46:29.610 --> 00:46:31.499
